            "value": "按拍摄、客户或交付批次组织导入照片。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Import will later default to the active session, so sessions can become the project boundary for CV recommendations, batch LUT application, and export delivery.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Import will later default to the active session, so sessions can become the project boundary for CV recommendations, batch LUT application, and export delivery."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "后续导入会默认进入当前会话，会话会成为视觉推荐、批量套 LUT 和导出交付的项目边界。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Only empty sessions can be deleted. Photos are never removed from here.": {
